- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on evaluating wireless communications over cellular networks.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of drones for wireless communications.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as the paper may touch on security concerns related to drone communications over cellular networks.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper evaluates TCP and UDP throughput, which are important for multimedia applications.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of a measurement tool for tracking GPS position.
